text: Chang Chenchen (born 20 June 1986) is a female Chinese international table tennis player. She won the bronze medal at the 2009 World Table Tennis Championships – Mixed Doubles with Hao Shuai. ==See also== * List of table tennis players ==References== Category:Table tennis players from Anshan Category:Living people Category:1986 births Category:Chinese female table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists Category:Chinese expatriate sportspeople in Japan Category:Expatriate table tennis people in Japan
